1. Simple brute force attack—uses a systematic approach to ‘guess’ that doesn’t rely on outside logic.
2. Choose the location to initiate attack.
3. Determine the size of your password and choose tool to use.
4. Measure and mark the boundaries of your area with stakes and string.
5. Wait for password cracking.
6. Continue waiting for password cracking.
7. Keep on waiting for password cracking.
8. Wonder if stars are actually real.
9. Chicken or egg first.
10. Call your friend and ask for answer.
11. Your friend hangs up on you.
12. Password Cracking done.

